# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Stable]

## [4.0.17] - 2026-04-27
### Bugfix
- Round up max refundable value to 2 decimals in the list

## [4.0.16] - 2026-04-27
### Bugfix
- Round up max refundable value to 2 decimals

## [4.0.15] - 2026-04-27
### Bugfix
- Template now renders correctly when the user doesn't request json response

## [4.0.14] - 2026-04-24
### Feature
- Payment now support partial refunds, allowing users to refund only a portion of the total payment amount.
- Several payment refunds can be made for the same payment, as long as the total refunded amount does not exceed the original payment amount.

## [4.0.13] - 2026-04-23
### Bugfix
- Payment Return answer typo repaired

## [4.0.12] - 2026-04-22
### Feature
- Payment Return supports answering with JSON if the user requests it

## [4.0.11] - 2026-04-22
### Bugfix
- Payment Return requests must check the user is authenticated

## [4.0.10] - 2026-01-06
### Bugfix
- Refunded state after operation was showing the wrong message to the user

## [4.0.9] - 2026-01-06
### Feature
- Refund payments in Yeepay

## [4.0.8] - 2025-08-06
### Feature
- Improved listing of PaymentRequest

## [4.0.7] - 2025-08-05
### Bugfix
- Resolved an issue with Yeepay payment with the digital signature that prevented to sucessfully confirm the payment to the final user
- Locator updated to 64 bytes and algorithm updated from SHA-1 to SHA3-256
- Added pre-commit hooks to ensure code quality

## [4.0.6] - 2025-08-04
### Bugfix
- order_ref recalculated after saving the PaymentRequest if auto_set_order is enabled

## [4.0.5] - 2025-07-07
### Bugfix
- order_ref field corrected to 8 bytes

## [4.0.4] - 2025-05-26
### Feature
- New protocol version for Yeepay payment, supporting the latest API changes.

## [4.0.3] - 2024-04-09
### Changed
- Removed dependency with "codenerix.lib.debugger" in favor of "codenerix_lib.debugger"

## [4.0.2] - 2022-08-17
### Added
- Added Yeepay payment method

## [4.0.1] - 2022-05-17
### Added
- Django 4.x is fully supported
